  "title": "AdaPaxels",
  "description": "A multitool which combines pickaxe, axe and shovel. Can make Paths and strip logs.",
  "body": "<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"143\" height=\"48\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">AdaPaxels is a mod made using Fabric API. It adds a multitool which combines pickaxe, axe and shovel.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Vanilla Paxels were originally in my mod <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/adabranium\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>Adabranium</strong>.</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This mod adds Paxels which are tools combining blocks that can be mined by a pickaxe, an axe, a shovel and a hoe.&nbsp;They can also make paths strip logs with right click.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">A paxel has 3x base durability.</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;For example, an iron pickaxe have 250 durability so the paxel will have 750.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q1j84to.png\" width=\"450\" height=\"198\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Netherite Paxel can also be crafted using Stacked Netherite (crafted with 3 Ingots) with a Diamond Paxel &amp; a Netherite Upgrade in a Smithing Table.</span></p>\n<hr>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Vanilla Paxels</strong></span></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Wooden, Stone, </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Golden, Copper, </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Iron,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Diamond,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Netherite</span></p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Modded Paxels</strong></span></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/techreborn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Tech Reborn</a></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">: </span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Bronze,&nbsp;Ruby, Sapphire, Peridot</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/adabranium\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Adabranium</a> :&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Nether, Vibranium, Adamantium&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/enderite-mod-for-fabric\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Enderite Mod</a>: </span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Enderite</span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/dragonloot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">DragonLoot</a></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dragonloot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">:</a></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> </span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Dragon</span></span></span></span></p>",
